cret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Last time, she fought in a Sonoro Sphere tainted by the <te href=851023>Dark Tide</te>. This may explain why she felt the Threnodian's pull growing stronger.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Trust in science for a simpler solution, Miss Cartethyia.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"For now, she should avoid using her Forte.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Based on the data you sent back, the Inverted Tower may be the ideal place for her recovery.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Yes. That Sonoro Sphere's formation is connected to Imperator, which should help stabilize Cartethyia's energy.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Also, during her examination earlier, Cartethyia sensed traces of the Leviathan's residual energy again.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"We're narrowing down the search. Once we have a location, we'll inform you immediately.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"…Understood. I'll notify our contact to arrange transport for you.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Please be very careful.","quest_name":"Dreamcatchers in the Secret Gardens","quest_id":171000004},{"text":"Finally! {PlayerName}, we've been trying to reach you, but we kept losing the connection.","quest_name":"The Present and the Future","quest_id":171700002},{"text":"That's a relief. You mentioned the seabed. Have you discovered anything?","quest_name":"The Present and the Future","quest_id":171700002},{"text":"You mean the <te href=851027>Threnodian's Gem</te> caused the Dark Tide? But we didn't detect any anomalous frequencies in Rinascita.","quest_name":"The Present and the Future","quest_id":171700002},{"text":"Please take care of yourself. We'll keep you updated with any developments.","quest_name":"The Present and the Future","quest_id":171700002},{"text":"Hello, {PlayerName}, what brings you here?","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000},{"text":"Oh? But Lady Flora's item was already picked up by another Bloom Bearer.","quest_name":"Forking Paths Among the Stars","quest_id":886000000}]}